Here's how it works - Octo can program Red Creatures...
Like this one...
Octo controls all the rutilious... err... red creatures!
Red fish come in, take a Starfish, and leave.
You have to reprogram them...
But you'll need pearls to do that ! Pearls come from Mercenaria mercenaria! Er... clams! Just tap a pearl to pick it up.
Kodu appreciates the help!
With enough pearls, you can buy a Fortress. Fortresses undo Octo's programming. Tap or click the Green "Breaker" button.
Now you can buy a tower. Towers will wake our friends up. Tap or Click the Green 'Stunner' button.

Now, lets take a look at the Power Strip. See the red glow? Tap or click on it.
Power Strips push creatures down different paths. This can be a big help in an altercation... er... battle!
The current pushes the turtle down the new path. My, those Testudinidae... err... turtles are tough.
Turtles are harder to de-program than Fish.
